e-template=\"%s su 5 stelle\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Di <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sutailia/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/87c270fdbc635d102ff349701a2cddf5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/87c270fdbc635d102ff349701a2cddf5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sutailia/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">sutailia</a> il <span class=\"review-date\">Giugno 17, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We\'ve used this plugin on several sites.  The plugin is frequently glitchy, they don\'t update code to keep up with other major themes/plugins, and their support is completely non existent.  And they takes weeks to respond to support tickets just to tell you to do things you already did and if that doesn\'t work to go to the forums, which was already done.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>They will also nickel and dime you with every single tiny feature.  Seriously, don\'t waste your time and find other options.  There are a ton.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Outstanding Plugin and Exceptional Support Team</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 su 5 stelle\" data-title-template=\"%s su 5 stelle\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Di <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/miky990t/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d8e1420f033017f3ab84234427da1b15?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d8e1420f033017f3ab84234427da1b15?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/miky990t/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">miky990t</a> il <span class=\"review-date\">Giugno 16, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I\'ve been using the WooCommerce plugin for my online store, and I couldn\'t be more satisfied. The plugin is incredibly user-friendly, flexible, and packed with features that make managing my e-commerce site a breeze. What truly sets WooCommerce apart, though, is their support team. Whenever I\'ve had questions or needed assistance, they\'ve been prompt, knowledgeable, and extremely helpful. They go above and beyond to ensure all my issues are resolved quickly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:174:\"Tutto ci di cui hai bisogno per lanciare un negozio online in pochi giorni e farlo crescere per anni. Woo ti accompagna dalla tua prima vendita a quando fatturerai milioni.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.9.0.2.zip\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:0:{}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:6:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=2366418\";s:7:\"caption\";s