t-color\" style=\"color:#000000;font-size:6vw;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:0.9;text-decoration:none;text-transform:none\">Crescita positiva.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:1vw\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-vertical is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-60 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-5 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.38%\">\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#000000;font-size:17px\"><em>Nature</em>, in the common sense, refers to essences unchanged by man; space, the air, the river, the leaf.&nbsp;<em>Art</em>&nbsp;is applied to the mixture of his will with the same things, as in a house, a canal, a statue, a picture. </p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#000000;font-size:17px\">But his operations taken together are so insignificant, a little chipping, baking, patching, and washing, that in an impression so grand as that of the world on the human mind, they do not vary the result.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33%\">\n<div style=\"height:2vw\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/5.8/outside-01.jpg\" alt=\"Il sole che tramonta attraverso una fitta foresta di alberi.\" /></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.62%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/5.8/outside-02.jpg\" alt=\"Turbine eoliche in piedi su una pianura erbosa, con un cielo blu sullo sfondo.\" /></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-6 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:69%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/5.8/outside-03.jpg\" alt=\"Il sole splende su un crinale che conduce alla costa. In lontananza, un\'auto scende lungo una strada.\" /></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33%\">\n<div style=\"height:2vw\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#000000;font-size:17px\">Indubbiamente non abbiamo domande da porre senza risposta. Dobbiamo fidarci della perfezione della creazione fino a questo punto, da credere che qualunque curiosit l&#8217;ordine delle cose ha risvegliato nelle nostre menti, l&#8217;ordine delle cose pu soddisfare. La condizione di ogni uomo  una soluzione in geroglifico a quelle domande che avrebbe posto.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\";s:9:\"protected\";b:0;}s:4:\"meta\";O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:13:\"wpop_keywords\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"wpop_description\";s:83:\"Tre colonne con immagini e testo, con spaziatura verticale per un aspetto sfalsato.\";s:19:\"wpop_viewport_width\";i:1200;s:16:\"wpop_block_types\";a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}s:11:\"wpop_locale\";s:5:\"it_IT\";s:15:\"wpop_wp_version\";s:0:\"\";s:25:\"wpop_contains_block_types\";s:86:\"core/column,core/columns,core/group,core/heading,core/image,core/paragraph,core/spacer\";s:9:\"footnotes\";s:0:\"\";}s:14:\"category_slugs\";a:5:{i:0;s:7:\"columns\";i:1;s:8:\"featured\";i:2;s:7:\"gallery\";i:3;s:6:\"images\";i:4;s:4:\"text\";}s:13:\"keyword_slugs\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"core\";i:1;s:8:\"featured\";}